title: Independent Candidate Misbah Wajid wins PP-172 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Independent candidate Misbah Wajid won the Punjab Assembly elections from PP-172, Lahore -XXVIII by securing 313,78 votes.
According to unofficial results, issued by the returning officer/ECP, the runner-up was Pakistan Muslim League Rana Mashood Ahmed Khan who bagged 28,647 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turnout remained 41.30 percent.
